  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK944">
<l>aṟṟa taṟintu kaṭaippiṭittu māṟalla</l>
<l>tuykka tuvarap pacittu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>(First) assure yourself that your food has been digested and never fail to eat, when very hungry, whatever is not disagreeable (to you).</l>
            </lg>
